<h1>VoiceTel Phone</h1>
<p class="lede">One app, three form factors — same crystal-clear calling. SIP-over-TLS, WebRTC, DTMF, caller ID, call history, recording, and real-time SIP message logging for diagnostics.</p>

<p>Available on web (no install), desktop (Windows / macOS / Linux), and mobile (iOS / Android). Sign in with your VoiceTel SIP credentials provisioned in the portal.</p>

